We always enjoyed this bar, however today we visited, and one of our party accidentally left a bag at our table, and the response from the bar was shocking.

We went to the toilet and came back to the table and the bag was missing! Furthermore, when we asked the staff if they’d seen the bag, the ability to converse in English evaporated from the same staff that had been serving us in English comfortably all afternoon.

Very disappointing. It was only an item of clothing from a nearby shop, but it could be any possession for future visitors… be very careful.
